Scope of our Project
There is no such dedicated platform for Fancy farming business. Fancy World will fill that gap in 
the market and will serve as a platform which will connect all relevant people in this business. In 
that way with the help of this new platform it will be easy for newbies to observe market trends 
and demand. All Fancy Farming businesses will get an opportunity to connect with other existing 
businesses. Users will be able to post about new breeds and their posts will be visible to other users 
which will help them understand market trend and demand.
